<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/commentary/op-ef13.html 204.71.237.74 19970108141524 text/html 5570
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 14:15:40 GMT
